{
  "stem": "25027.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I believe we were the only ones of all the Soviet nationalities that had on their Russian passport-- that was an internal passport, not an external-- that it said the religion of the Jew.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody else had that on the-- on the--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of the were, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't think I ran into anti-Semitism before 1941, as a civilian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We thought that some of them might have been anti-Semitic, but this was very hard to pinpoint exactly what-- what transpired.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many of the Jews were arrested because, you know, the only way to make a living in Poland, and here the Russians came in, is by trading-- you buy something, you sell something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called it black marketeering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no jobs to be available for the general population when the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were a few government jobs, but the only way you could, for the first year or two, to-- to make a living is to continue what you did before, you know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was considered black marketeering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So many of them were arrested, thrown in jail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To us, it was anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To them, it was black marketeering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They called it a different name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the better, we were still the same, except we couldn't to receive the packages and the money from the United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was tougher.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mother became an official teacher for a kindergarten class, and was paid some rubles by the government, and that's how we survived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because she was running this-- this kindergarten-like type of school-- it wasn't hers anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a town-run school, and she became a teacher, which was paid a few rubles by-- by whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember how many or what.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
